::DarkMouse::

She left the console and walked back to the lab.  She started 
cleaning it up again.  She looked at the box that was sitting on the 
counter.  She sighed and went back to tidying up the viles and the 
lab tables.  She would have to replace the straps ont he table since 
they were broken.  She went over to the closet and got out another 
set of the straps.  she reattached them to the table and reset the 
controls for the table.  She then went over to the other corner were 
the controls for the autoguns were inside the lab.  She reset them so 
they were operational again.

She finished cleaning up and went back to her console.  She sat down 
at her computer and looked at the link controls. So far, no one has 
reported in and no responce yet from Zardus.
